profile.name: TopDiff
profile.bio: I'm a top laner who loves to play tanks and bruisers.

keystone.name: Lethal Tempo
keystone.shortDesc: 1.5s after damaging a champion gain a large amount of Attack Speed. Lethal Tempo allows you to temporarily exceed the attack speed limit.
keystone.longDesc: 1.5s after damaging a champion gain 40 - 110% Attack Speed (based on level) for 3s. Attacking a champion extends the effect to 6s.
